      <title>一建笔记-土石方施工1</title>
      <link href="/p/3e7746ad.html"/>
      <url>/p/3e7746ad.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>该部分知识点琐碎，考试分值至少 2分，可考选择题和案例题。考试难度居中，知识点以记忆为主。</p><h2 id="岩土的工程性能"><a href="#岩土的工程性能" class="headerlink" title="岩土的工程性能"></a>岩土的工程性能</h2><table><thead><tr><th align="center">指标名称</th><th align="center">用途</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">内摩擦角</td><td align="center">是土的抗剪强度指标，反映土或岩石内部各颗粒之间内摩擦力的大小。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">土抗剪强度</td><td align="center">包括内摩擦力和内聚力。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">天然含水量</td><td align="center">对挖土的难易、土方边坡的稳定、填土的压实等均有影响。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">干密度</td><td align="center">干密度越大，表明土越坚实。<strong>在土方填筑时，常以土的干密度控制土的夯实标准。</strong></td></tr><tr><td align="center">密实度</td><td align="center">土被固体颗粒所充实的程度，反映了土的紧密程度。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">土的可松性</td><td align="center">是挖填土方时，计算土方机械生成率、回填土方量、运输机具数量、进行场地平整规划竖向设计、土方平衡调配的重要参数。</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="例题"><a href="#例题" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h3><p>【例题·单选】关于岩土工程性能的说法，正确的是（ ）。【2014】</p><p>A.内摩擦角不是土体的抗剪强度指标</p><p>B.土体的抗剪强度指标包含有内摩擦力和内聚力</p><p>C.在土方填筑时，常以土的天然密度控制土的夯实标准</p><p>D.土的天然含水量对土体边坡稳定没有影响</p><p>【答案】B</p><p>【解析】土的内摩擦角是土的抗剪强度指标；土方填筑时，常以土的干密实度控制土的夯实标准；土的天然含水量对挖土的难易、土方边坡的稳定、填土的压实等均有影响。</p><h2 id="基坑支护施工"><a href="#基坑支护施工" class="headerlink" title="基坑支护施工"></a>基坑支护施工</h2><p>《建筑基坑支护技术规程》JGJ120—2012 规定，基坑侧壁的安全等级分为<strong>一级、二级和三级，</strong>不同等级采用相对应的重要性系数γ<sub>0</sub>，（详见下表）。</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">安全等级</th><th align="center">破坏后果</th><th align="center">重要性系数</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">一级</td><td align="center">支护结构失效、土体过大变形对基坑周边环境或主体结构施工安全的影响<strong>很严重</strong></td><td align="center">1.10</td></tr><tr><td align="center">二级</td><td align="center">支护结构失效、土体过大变形对基坑周边环境或主体结构施工安全的影响<strong>严重</strong></td><td align="center">1.00</td></tr><tr><td align="center">三级</td><td align="center">支护结构失效、土体过大变形对基坑周边环境或主体结构施工安全的影响<strong>不严重</strong></td><td align="center">0.90</td></tr></tbody></table><ul><li><strong>一级基坑</strong>为符合下列情况之一<ol><li>重要工程或支护结构做主体结构的一部分；</li><li>开挖深度大于<strong>10m</strong>；</li><li>与邻近建筑物，重要设施的距离在开挖深度以内的基坑，即：水平距离 S＜开挖深度 H；</li><li>基坑范围内有历史文物、近代优秀建筑、重要管线等须严加保护的基坑。</li></ol></li><li><strong>二级基坑</strong><ol><li>开挖深度小于<strong>7m</strong>，且周围环境无特别要求时的基坑。</li></ol></li><li><strong>三级基坑</strong><ol><li>除一级和三级外的基坑。</li></ol></li></ul><h3 id="浅基坑支护（5m-以内，易考选择题）"><a href="#浅基坑支护（5m-以内，易考选择题）" class="headerlink" title="浅基坑支护（5m 以内，易考选择题）"></a>浅基坑支护（5m 以内，易考选择题）</h3><h4 id="斜柱支撑"><a href="#斜柱支撑" class="headerlink" title="斜柱支撑"></a>斜柱支撑</h4><p>水平挡土板钉在柱桩内侧，柱桩外侧用斜撑支顶，斜撑底端支在木桩上， 在挡土板内侧回填土。<strong>适于开挖较大型、深度不大的基坑或使用机械挖土时。</strong></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p1.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p1.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="斜柱支撑"></p><h4 id="锚拉支撑"><a href="#锚拉支撑" class="headerlink" title="锚拉支撑"></a>锚拉支撑</h4><p>水平挡土板支在柱桩的内侧，柱桩一端打入土中，另一端用拉杆与锚桩拉紧，在挡土板内侧回填土。<strong>适于开挖较大型、深度较深的基坑或使用机械挖土，不能安设横撑时使用。</strong></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p2.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p2.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="锚拉支撑"></p><h4 id="型钢桩横挡板支撑"><a href="#型钢桩横挡板支撑" class="headerlink" title="型钢桩横挡板支撑"></a>型钢桩横挡板支撑</h4><p>沿挡土位置预先打入钢轨、工字钢或 H 型钢桩，间距 1.0～1.5m， 然后边挖方，边将 3～6cm 厚的挡土板塞进钢桩之间挡土，并在横向挡板与型钢桩之间打上楔子，使横板与土体紧密接触。<strong>适于地下水位较低、深度不很大的一般黏性或砂土层中使用。</strong></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p3.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p3.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="型钢桩横挡板支撑"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p4.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p4.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="型钢桩横挡板支撑"></p><h4 id="短桩横隔板支撑"><a href="#短桩横隔板支撑" class="headerlink" title="短桩横隔板支撑"></a>短桩横隔板支撑</h4><p>打入小短木桩或钢桩，部分打入土中，部分露出地面，钉上水平挡土板， 在背面填土、夯实。适于开挖宽度大的基坑，<strong>当部分地段下部放坡不够时使用。</strong></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p5.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p5.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="短桩横隔板支撑"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p6.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p6.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="短桩横隔板支撑"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p7.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p7.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="短桩横隔板支撑"></p><h4 id="临时挡土墙支撑"><a href="#临时挡土墙支撑" class="headerlink" title="临时挡土墙支撑"></a>临时挡土墙支撑</h4><p>沿坡脚用砖、石叠砌或用装水泥的聚丙烯扁丝编织袋、草袋装土、砂堆砌，使坡脚保持稳定。适于开挖宽度大的基坑，<strong>当部分地段下部放坡不够时使用。</strong></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p8.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p8.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="临时挡土墙支撑"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p9.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p9.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="临时挡土墙支撑"></p><h4 id="挡土灌注桩支护"><a href="#挡土灌注桩支护" class="headerlink" title="挡土灌注桩支护"></a>挡土灌注桩支护</h4><p>在开挖基坑的周围，用钻机或洛阳铲成孔，桩径 400～500mm，现场灌注钢筋混凝土桩，桩间距为 1.0～1.5m，将桩间土方挖成外拱形，使之起土拱作用。<strong>适用于开挖较大、较浅（小于 5m）基坑，邻近有建筑物，不允许背面地基有下沉、位移时采用。</strong></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p10.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p10.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="挡土灌注桩支护"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p11.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p11.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="挡土灌注桩支护"></p><h4 id="叠袋式挡墙支护"><a href="#叠袋式挡墙支护" class="headerlink" title="叠袋式挡墙支护"></a>叠袋式挡墙支护</h4><p>采用编织袋或草袋装碎石（砂砾石或土）堆砌成重力式挡墙作为基坑的支护，在墙下部砌 500mm 厚块石基础，墙底宽 1500～2000mm，顶宽适当放坡卸土 1.0～ 1.5m，表面抹砂浆保护。<strong>适用于一般黏性土、面积大、开挖深度应在 5m 以内的浅基坑支护。</strong></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p12.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p12.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="叠袋式挡墙支护"></p><h4 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h4><table><thead><tr><th align="center"><strong>支护类型</strong></th><th align="center"><strong>适应范围</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">斜柱支撑</td><td align="center">适于开挖较大型、深度不大的基坑或使用机械挖土时。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">锚拉支撑</td><td align="center">适于开挖较大型、深度较深的基坑或使用机械挖土，不能安设横撑时使用。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">型钢桩横挡板支撑</td><td align="center">适于地下水位较低、深度不很大的一般黏性或砂土层中使用。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">短桩横隔板支撑</td><td align="center">适于开挖宽度大的基坑，当部分地段下部放坡不够时使用。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">临时挡土墙支撑</td><td align="center">适于开挖宽度大的基坑，当部分地段下部放坡不够时使用。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">挡土灌注桩支护</td><td align="center">适用于开挖较大、较浅（小于 5m）基坑，邻近有建筑物，不允许背面地基有下沉、位移时采用。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">叠袋式挡墙支护</td><td align="center">适用于一般黏性土、面积大、开挖深度应在 5m 以内的浅基坑支护。</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="深基坑支护"><a href="#深基坑支护" class="headerlink" title="深基坑支护"></a>深基坑支护</h3><p>基坑开挖深度大于等于 5m 或小于 5m 但现场地质情况和周围环境较复杂的基坑工程，以及其他需要监测的基坑工程应实施基坑监测。基坑监测应由建设方委托具有相应资质的第三方实施。基坑监测应包括对支护结构、已施工的主体结构和邻近的道路、市政管线、地下设施、周围建（构）筑物等项目进行监测。</p><p><strong>注意可考案例简答题</strong></p><p>基坑支护结构的类型有灌注桩排桩围护墙、板桩围护墙、咬合桩围护墙、型钢水泥土搅拌墙、地下连续墙、水泥土重力式围护墙、土钉墙等；支护结构围护墙的支撑形式有内支撑、锚杆（索）、与主体结构相结合（两墙合一）的基坑支护等。</p><h4 id="灌注桩排桩支护"><a href="#灌注桩排桩支护" class="headerlink" title="灌注桩排桩支护"></a>灌注桩排桩支护</h4><p>通常由支护桩、支撑（或土层锚杆）及防渗帷幕等组成。排桩根据支撑情况可分为悬臂式支护结构、锚拉式支护结构、内撑式支护结构和内撑-锚拉混合式支护结构。当以上支护方式都不适合时，可以考虑采用双排桩形式。</p><p>适用条件：基坑侧壁安全等级为一级、二级、三级；适用于可采取降水或止水帷幕的基坑。除悬臂式支护适用于浅基坑外，其他几种支护方式都适用于深基坑。</p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p13.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p13.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="灌注桩排桩支"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p14.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p14.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="灌注桩排桩支"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p15.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p15.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="灌注桩排桩支"></p><ul><li>施工要求有<ol><li>灌注桩排桩应采取间隔成桩的施工顺序，已完成浇筑混凝土的桩与邻桩间距应大于 4 倍桩径，或间隔施工时间应大于 36h。</li><li>灌注桩顶应充分泛浆，高度不应小于 500mm；水下灌注混凝土时混凝土强度应比设计桩身强度提高一个强度等级进行配制。（例如设计 C30，配制按 C35）</li><li>灌注桩外截水帷幕宜采用单轴、双轴或三轴水泥土搅拌桩；截水帷幕与灌注桩排桩间的净距宜小于 200mm；采用高压旋喷桩时，应先施工灌注桩，再施工高压旋喷截水帷幕。</li></ol></li></ul><h4 id="地下连续墙支护"><a href="#地下连续墙支护" class="headerlink" title="地下连续墙支护"></a>地下连续墙支护</h4><p>地下连续墙可与内支撑、与主体结构相结合（两墙合一）等支撑形式采用顺作法、逆作法、半逆作法结合使用，施工振动小、噪声低，墙体刚度大，<strong>防渗性能好，对周围地基扰动小</strong>，可以组成具有很大承载力的连续墙。地下连续墙宜同时用作主体地下结构外墙即“两墙合一”。</p><p>适用条件：基坑侧壁安全等级为一级、二级、三级；适用于周边环境条件很复杂的深基坑。</p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p16.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p16.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="地下连续墙支护"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p17.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p17.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="地下连续墙支护"></p><ul><li>导墙施工要求有<ol><li>应设置现浇钢筋混凝土导墙。混凝土强度等级不应低于 C20，厚度不应小于 200mm；</li><li>导墙顶面应高于地面 100mm，高于地下水位 0.5m 以上；</li><li>导墙底部应进入原状土 200mm 以上；</li><li>导墙高度不应小于 1.2m；</li><li>导墙内净距应比地下连续墙设计厚度加宽 40mm（成槽机便于施工）。</li></ol></li></ul><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p19.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p19.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="地下连续墙施工"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p20.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p20.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="地下连续墙施工"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p21.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p21.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="导墙钢筋绑扎"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p22.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p22.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="导墙施工成品"></p><p>地下连续墙成槽前先要构筑导墙，导墙是保证地下连续墙位置准确和成槽质量的关键，在施工期间，导墙经常承受钢筋笼、浇注砼用的导管、钻机等静、动荷载的作用，因而必须认真设计和施工，才能进行地下连续墙的正式施工。</p><ul><li>导墙的作用<ol><li>给成槽机成槽提供导向，并承受挖槽机械的荷载；</li><li>储存泥浆和防止槽口土壁坍塌；</li><li>作为施工时水平与垂直测量的基准；</li><li>为钢筋笼安放、混凝土导管安置、成槽机提供标定；</li><li>保证地下连续墙设计的几何尺寸和形状。</li></ol></li></ul><p>地下连续墙单元槽段长度宜为 4～6m。槽内泥浆面不应低于导墙面 0.3m，同时应高于地下水位 0.5m 以上。</p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p23.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p23.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="地下连续墙"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p24.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p24.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="地下连续墙施工流程"></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p19-16290333384861.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p19-16290333384861.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="开挖沟槽"></p><p>水下混凝土应采用导管法连续浇筑。导管水平布置距离不应大于 3m，距槽段端部不应大于 1.5m，导管下端距槽底宜为 300～500mm；钢筋笼吊放就位后应及时浇筑混凝土，间隔不宜大于 4h；现场混凝土坍落度宜为 200±20mm，<strong>强度等级应比设计强度提高一级进行配制；混凝土浇筑面宜高出设计标高 300～500mm。</strong></p><p><img src="/p/3e7746ad/p25.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/3e7746ad/p25.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="地下连续墙浇筑"></p><p>混凝土达到设计强度后方可进行墙底注浆。注浆管应采用钢管；单元槽段内不少于 2 根，槽段长度大于 6m 时宜增加注浆管；注浆管下端应伸到槽底 200～500mm；注浆压力应控制在2MPa 以内，注浆总量达到设计要求或注浆量达到 80%以上且压力达到 2MPa 可终止注浆。</p>]]></content>
      
      
