        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>该部分知识比较简单，每年必考，分值 1-5 分不等。在历年真题中多考选择题，偶尔也考案例题。</p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p1.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p1.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="p1"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p2.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p2.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="p2"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p3.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p3.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="p3"></p><h2 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h2><ul><li><p>测量工作</p><ul><li>把设计图纸上工程建筑物的平面位置和高程，用一定的测量仪器和方法测设到 实地上去的测量工作，也称施工放线。</li></ul></li><li><p>测量控制点</p><ul><li><p>是指在进行测量作业之前，在要进行测量的区域范围内，布设一系列的点来 完成对整个区域的测量作业，在选点时，首先调查收集测区已有的地形图和控制点的成果资料。</p></li><li><p>水准点</p><ul><li>高程控制点通常以水准测量的方法建立，称为水准点。</li></ul></li><li><p>全国统一高程基准面</p><ul><li>中国高度从这里开始：黄海平均海水面为“全国统一高程基准面“</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p4.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p4.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="全国统一高程基准面"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p5.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p5.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="国家水准点"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p6.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p6.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="高程点标志"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p7.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p7.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="永久高程点"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p8.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p8.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="高程测量"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p9.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p9.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="全站仪测量"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p10.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p10.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="放线"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p11.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p11.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="全站仪测量"></p><h2 id="施工测量的基本工作"><a href="#施工测量的基本工作" class="headerlink" title="施工测量的基本工作"></a>施工测量的基本工作</h2><p>施工测量现场主要工作有，对长度、角度、建筑物细部点平面位置、建筑物细部点高程位置及倾斜线的测设等。测角、测距和测高差是测量的基本工作。</p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p12-16289481247061.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p12-16289481247061.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="水准仪"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p13.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p13.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="经纬仪和全站仪"></p><h2 id="常用测量仪器的性能与应用"><a href="#常用测量仪器的性能与应用" class="headerlink" title="常用测量仪器的性能与应用"></a>常用测量仪器的性能与应用</h2><table><thead><tr><th align="center">分类</th><th align="center">主要功能</th><th align="center">注意事项</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">水准仪</td><td align="center">测量高差（垂直距离）</td><td align="center">1.不能直接测量待定点的高程，但可由控制点的已知高程来推算测点的高程。<br> 2.利用视距测量原理，它可以测量两点间的<strong>水平距离</strong>。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">经纬仪</td><td align="center">测量角度（水平角+竖直角）</td><td align="center">可以借助水准尺，利用视距测量原理，测出两点间的<strong>水平距离和高差</strong></td></tr><tr><td align="center">全站仪</td><td align="center">角度测量和距离测量</td><td align="center">可在<strong>同一瞬间</strong>测得平距、高差、点的坐标和高程。</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p14.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p14.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="塔尺"></p><h3 id="例题"><a href="#例题" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h3><p>【例题·单选】关于工程测量仪器性能与应用的说法,正确的是( )。【2019】</p><p>A.水准仪可直接测量待定点高程</p><p>B.S3 型水准仪可用于国家三等水准测量</p><p>C.经纬仪不可以测量竖直角</p><p>D.激光经纬仪不能在夜间进行测量工作</p><p>【答案】B</p><p>【解析】水准仪的主要功能是测量两点间的高差，它不能直接测量待定点的高程，但可由控制点的已知高程来推算测点的高程，A 错误；S3 型水准仪称为普通水准仪，用于国家三、四等水准测量及一般工程水准测量，B 正确；经纬仪是对水平角和竖直角进行测量的一种仪器，C 错误；激光经纬仪能在夜间或黑暗的场地进行测量工作，不受照度的影响，D 错误。</p><hr><p>【例题·单选】工程测量用水准仪的主要功能是（ ）。【2010】</p><p>A.直接测量待定点的高程</p><p>B.测量两个方向之间的水平夹角</p><p>C.测量两点间的高差</p><p>D.直接测量竖直角</p><p>【答案】C</p><p>【解析】水准仪的主要功能是测量两点间的高差。</p><hr><p>【例题·单选】下列测量仪器中，最适宜用于多点间水平距离测量的是（ ）。【2015】</p><p>A.水准仪</p><p>B.经纬仪</p><p>C.激光铅直仪</p><p>D.全站仪</p><p>【答案】D</p><p>【解析】全站仪一般用于大型工程的场地坐标测设及复杂工程的定位和细部测设。</p><h2 id="建筑物细部点平面位置的测设"><a href="#建筑物细部点平面位置的测设" class="headerlink" title="建筑物细部点平面位置的测设"></a>建筑物细部点平面位置的测设</h2><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p15.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p15.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="平面图坐标点"></p><h3 id="直角坐标法"><a href="#直角坐标法" class="headerlink" title="直角坐标法"></a>直角坐标法</h3><p>当建筑场地的施工控制网为<strong>方格网或轴线形式</strong>时，采用直角坐标法放线最为方便。</p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p16.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p16.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="指教坐标法"></p><h3 id="极坐标法"><a href="#极坐标法" class="headerlink" title="极坐标法"></a>极坐标法</h3><p>极坐标法适用于<strong>测设点靠近控制点，便于量距的地方。</strong>用极坐标法测定一点的平面位置时，系<strong>在一个控制点上进行</strong>，但该点必须与另一控制点通视。</p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p17.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p17.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="极坐标法"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p18.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p18.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="数据计算"></p><h3 id="角度前方交会法"><a href="#角度前方交会法" class="headerlink" title="角度前方交会法"></a>角度前方交会法</h3><p>角度前方交会法，适用于<strong>不便量距或测设点远离控制点</strong>的地方。对于一般小型建筑物或 管线的定位，亦可采用此法。</p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p19.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p19.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="角度前方交会法"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p20.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p20.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="数据计算"></p><h3 id="距离交会法"><a href="#距离交会法" class="headerlink" title="距离交会法"></a>距离交会法</h3><p>用距离交会法来测定点位，不需要使用仪器，但精度较低。</p><p>先根据已知 A、B 点和待测点 P 的坐标，用坐标反算公式求出水平距离。测设时分别以 A、B 为中心，a、b 为半径，在场地上作弧线，两弧的交点即为 P。</p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p21.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p21.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="距离交会法"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p22.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p22.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="距离交会法"></p><h3 id="方向线交会法"><a href="#方向线交会法" class="headerlink" title="方向线交会法"></a>方向线交会法</h3><p>这种方法的特点是：测定点由相对应的两已知点或两定向点的方向线交会而得。方向线的设 立可以用经纬仪，也可以用细线绳。</p><p>方向线法放样是利用两条相互垂直的方向线相交来定出放样点平面位置的一种放样方法。采 用此方法放样时，需要有矩形建筑方格网。</p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p23.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p23.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="方向线交会法"></p><h3 id="方法总结"><a href="#方法总结" class="headerlink" title="方法总结"></a>方法总结</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="center">测量方法</th><th align="center">适用范围</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">直角坐标法</td><td align="center">当建筑场地的施工<strong>控制网为方格网或轴线形式</strong>时，采用直角坐标法放线最为方便。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">极坐标法</td><td align="center">极坐标法适用于<strong>测设点靠近控制点</strong>，便于量距的地方。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">角度前方交会法</td><td align="center">适用于<strong>不便量距或测设点远离控制点</strong>的地方。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">距离交会法</td><td align="center">不需要使用仪器，但精度较低。</td></tr><tr><td align="center">方向线交会法</td><td align="center">测定点由相对应的两已知点或两定向点的方向线交会而得。方向线的设立可以用经纬仪，也可以用细线绳。</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="例题-1"><a href="#例题-1" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h3><p>【例题·单选】依据建筑场地的施工控制方格网放线，最为方便的方法是( )。【2020】【2014】</p><p>A.极坐标法</p><p>B.角度前方交会法</p><p>C.直角坐标法</p><p>D.方向线交会法</p><p>【答案】C</p><p>【解析】当建筑场地的施工控制网为方格网或轴线形式时，采用直角坐标法放线最为方便。</p><h2 id="建筑物细部点高程位置的测设"><a href="#建筑物细部点高程位置的测设" class="headerlink" title="建筑物细部点高程位置的测设"></a>建筑物细部点高程位置的测设</h2><p>建筑物高程控制，应采用<strong>水准测量</strong>。附合线路闭合差，不应低于四等水准的要求，水准点的个数<strong>不应少于两个</strong>。高程控制点的高程值一般采用工程±0.000高程值。</p><p><strong>注意：水准测量的等级是根据国家水准网来定的。国家水准网布设成一等、二等、三等、四等4个等级。其布设原则采用从高级到低级，从整体到局部，分级布置，逐级加密的原则，等级划分是根据环线周长、附和路线长、偶然中误差、全中误差来分的。一、二等水准测量称为“精密水准测量”，是国家高程控制的全面基础，可为研究地壳形变等提供数据。三、四等水准测量直接为地形测图和各种工程建设提供所必需的高程控制。</strong></p><p>水准仪有：DS05，DS1， DS3， DS10，通常省略 D；</p><p>S05、S1 是精密水准仪，用以国家一、二等水准测量及其他精准测量；</p><p><strong>S3 是普通水准仪，用以国家三、四等水准测量及一般工程水准测量。</strong></p><p>测定地面上点的高程（如下图所示），设 B 为待测点，其设计高程为 H<sub>B</sub>,A 为水准点，已知其高程为 H<sub>A</sub>。测量步骤：</p><ol><li><p>安置水准仪于 A、B 之间，先在 A 点立尺，读得后视读数为 a</p></li><li><p>然后在 B 点立尺。升高或降低 B 点上所立之尺，使前视尺之读数等于 b。b 可按下式计算： H<sub>A</sub>+a=H<sub>B</sub>+b</p></li><li><p>当前视尺读数恰好等于 b 时，在木桩侧面沿水准尺底边画一横线，此线就是 B 点的设计高程。</p></li></ol><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p24.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p24.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="测定地面上点的高程"></p><h3 id="例题-2"><a href="#例题-2" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h3><p>【例题·单选】对某一施工现场进行高程测设，M 点为水准点，已知高程为 12.00m；N 点为待测点，安置水准仪于 M、N 之间，先在 M 点立尺，读得后视读数为 4.500m，然后在 N 点立尺，读得前视读数为 3.500m,N 点高程为（ ）m。【2012 二建案例、2010 年一建】</p><p>A.11.000 </p><p>B.12.000 </p><p>C.12.500 </p><p>D.13.000 </p><p>【答案】D</p><p>【解析】前视点高程+前视读数=后视高程+后视读数，H<sub>N</sub>=12.000+4.500-3.500=13.00（m）。</p><hr><p>【例题·案例题节选】【2014】</p><p>某新建办公楼在合同履行过程中，发生了下列事件：由于建设单位提供的高程基准点 A 点（高程 H<sub>A</sub> 为 75.141m）离基坑较远，项目技术负责人要求将高程控制点引测至临近基坑的 B 点。技术人员在两点间架设水准仪，A 点立尺读数 a 为 1.441m，B 点立尺度数 b 为 3.521m。</p><p>【问题】请列式计算 B 点高程 H<sub>B</sub>。</p><p>【参考答案】由 H<sub>A</sub>+a=H<sub>B</sub>+b 得：75.141+1.441=H<sub>B</sub>+3.521，H<sub>B</sub>=73.061m。</p><h2 id="建筑施工期间的变形测量"><a href="#建筑施工期间的变形测量" class="headerlink" title="建筑施工期间的变形测量"></a>建筑施工期间的变形测量</h2><ol><li><p>在施工期间应进行变形测量的有：</p><ol><li>地基基础设计等级为甲级的建筑；</li><li>软弱地基上的地基基础设计等级为乙级的建筑；</li><li>加层、扩建或处理地基上的建筑；</li><li>受邻近施工影响或受场地地下水等环境因素变化影响的建筑；</li><li>采用新型基础或新型结构的建筑；</li><li>大型城市基础设施；</li><li>体型狭长且地基土变化明显的建筑。</li></ol><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p25.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p25.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="变形测量"></p></li><li><p>建筑在施工期间的变形测量要求：</p><ol><li>对各类建筑应进行沉降观测，宜进行场地沉降观测、地基土分层沉降观测和斜坡位移观测。</li><li>对基坑工程应进行基坑及其支护结构变形观测和周边环境变形观测；对一级基坑应进行基坑回弹观测。</li><li>对高层和超高层建筑，应进行倾斜观测。</li><li>当建筑出现裂缝时，应进行裂缝观测。</li><li>施工需要时，进行其他类型的变形观测。</li></ol></li><li><p>建筑变形测量精度等级分为特等、一等、二等、三等、四等共五级。</p></li></ol><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p26.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p26.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="基坑"></p><p><img src="/p/41b3281b/p27.webp" class="lazyload" data-srcset="/p/41b3281b/p27.webp" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="基坑"></p>]]></content>
      
      
